        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Our Widows and Widowers in Retirement (POWR) Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases Social Security benefits for widows or widowers in two-income households by establishing an alternative method to calculate survivors benefits based on combined household benefit amounts.</p>]]>
